title: Ep. 89 - Oil's Ultimate Insider
itunes:title: Oil's Ultimate Insider
description: Dr. Kent Moors has been an advisor to major oil companies for more than three decades. He sits down with Frank to discuss where oil is heading, the huge potential in natural gas and his favorite energy picks.
